OL,3,CFinland schoolboy, 12, shot classmates
OL,4,Cover 'bullying' police say
OL,6,FA 12-year-old boy and killed his
OL,7,Fclassmate because he was being
OL,8,Fbullied, police in Finland have said.
OL,10,FIn a statement officers said: "The
OL,11,Fmotive for the act has been confirmed
OL,12,Fto be bullying.
OL,14,F"During questioning, the suspect has
OL,15,Fsaid that he has been the victim of
OL,16,Fbullying."
OL,18,FPolice said one of the wounded girls
OL,19,Fhas a dual Finland-Kosovo citizenship.
OL,20,FThe suspect and the victims were all
OL,21,Fclassmates.
