OL,4,Cover 'bullying' police say
OL,6,FMourners gathered outside the scene at
OL,7,FViertola Lower Secondary school in
OL,8,FVantaa, near Helsinki on Wednesday.
OL,10,FThe Finnish government declared a
OL,11,Fnationwide day of mourning on
OL,12,FWednesday, ordering all state agencies
OL,13,Fand institutions to lower the national
OL,14,Fflag to half-mast.
OL,16,FThe suspect was apprehended less than
OL,17,Fan hour after the attack, which
OL,18,Fhappened at around 7.08am BST on
OL,19,FTuesday.
