OL,3,CFinland schoolboy, 12, shot classmates
OL,4,Cover 'bullying' police say
OL,6,FIn a statement on Wednesday, police
OL,7,Fsaid the killing was carried out using
OL,8,F"a revolver-like handgun."
OL,10,FOne of the pupils died instantly after
OL,11,Fbeing shot, Chief of Police Ilkka
OL,12,FKoskimaki from the Eastern Uusimaa
OL,13,FPolice Department told a news
OL,14,Fconference.
OL,16,FThe other two were seriously wounded,
OL,17,Fhe added.
OL,19,FThe weapon used in the shooting was a
OL,20,Fregistered handgun that was licensed
OL,21,Fto the suspect's relative.
