OL,6,FHe admitted to the shooting in an
OL,7,Finitial police hearing, police said,
OL,8,Fadding that the case is being
OL,9,Finvestigated as a murder and two
OL,10,Fattempted murders.
OL,12,FThe minimum age of criminal liability
OL,13,Fin Finland is 15 years, which means
OL,14,Fthe suspect cannot be formally
OL,15,Farrested.
OL,17,FA suspect younger than 15 can only be
OL,18,Fheard by the police after which they
OL,19,Fwill be handed over to Finland's child
OL,20,Fwelfare authorities.
